# BeatWise – Testing

**Docs**: `docs/TESTING.md`

**Frontend**: Vitest + React Testing Library. Tests in `*.test.tsx` or `__tests__/`. Components, hooks, utils.

**Backend**: pytest. Units in `tests/`, fixtures in `conftest.py`. Test validation, normalization, tagging, API endpoints.

**API**: FastAPI TestClient. Test POST /upload (200, session_id), GET /status, GET /download. Mock LLM to avoid API costs.

**Fixtures**: Small MP3/WAV in `backend/tests/fixtures/`. Don't commit large files.

**Coverage Phase 0**: >60% on critical services. New code should include tests when applicable.
